{"tid":852574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"帶咗條女翻屋企，屋企人突然翻嚟［集思廣益］","createTime":"2018-10-08T03:01:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T08:25:50.000Z","uid":154157,"like":45,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"c7112ae1c1bf9c060629a36060c53516308df900","tid":852574,"uid":154157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:01:46.000Z","msg":"本身今日同條女都day off<br />\n諗住帶佢翻屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆街東鐵有人跳軌<br />\n延誤咗好多班車<br />\n跟著屋企人突然翻屋企<br />\n話請左上午嘅假<br />\n<br />\n條女依家重喺我張被入面<br />\n點撚算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n褲都除哂，想砌都冇得砌<br />\n利申 屋企唔大，間房係木板間出嚟<br />\n有冇巴打有方法救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9f810c6d0a3ee420477684c62970e3689615de","tid":852574,"uid":2757,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"下晝答你"},{"pid":"3a9eb4cdbf221781033c6049683f9e826783b877","tid":852574,"uid":154157,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:05:24.000Z","msg":"大家幫下手，到2點又有第二個屋企人會翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba84922f6ab129002cc4021310c211547cdfb7c","tid":852574,"uid":154157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf9f810c6d0a3ee420477684c62970e3689615de","tid":852574,"uid":2757,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"下晝答你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:06:26.000Z","msg":"屌你唔係咁殘忍下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a25a2cf1e43ccf60731fcf548453aa1f99b203","tid":852574,"uid":193613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T03:06:42.000Z","msg":"你住幾樓？"},{"pid":"2c250a19e0ee221ad9cd264d6c525a5f4